org.opendaylight.controller.sal.topology

Interface IPluginOutTopologyService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Topology

    public interface IPluginOutTopologyService
    This interface defines the methods that are invoked from Protocol Plugin toward SAL. Every time a protocol plugin update the topology, it will call this service provided by SAL so the update can migrate upward toward the applications.
